{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_01_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 背伸びしてる？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Turning back the clock…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.33333333333333326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストがデビューしてしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Shortly after Moon Tempest’s debut",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーむ……悩ましいですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*Hmm* That’s troubling…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "気高さと可憐さは超一級\n歩く姿は百合の花と名高い私とはいえ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Troubling even for me‚ one of superlative nobility and cuteness‚\nand resembling a lily in my walking deportment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "こればかりは解決の糸口が見えませんわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In just this matter I can’t see any clue to a solution…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "自画自賛しながら何を悩んでるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something’s bothering you as you sing your own praises?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "あら、{user}さん\n聞いていたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san.\nYou were listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてたんじゃなくて、勝手に聞こえてきたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn’t listening‚ but I happened to overhear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなのどっちでもいいですわ\n……そんなことより",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t care either way.\nMore to the point…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "あなた、長いこと星見プロに勤めているのですから\n長瀬麻奈様と面識はあったのですわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been working for Hoshimi Productions for a long time‚\nso may I assume you were acquainted with Mana Nagase?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、同じ事務所にいたから\n……そういえば、すずは麻奈に憧れてるんだっけか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I was in the same office‚ so…\n…Actually‚ Suzu‚ I gather you’re devoted to Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ。あの方に憧れない女の子は\nいないと言ってもいいでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. It’s fair to say there are no girls\nwho are not devoted to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "あの洗練されたダンス、素晴らしい歌唱力\n美しいお顔と、プロポー……ション……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her refined dancing and superb vocal power.\nHer beautiful face and pro… portions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "……決めましたわ{user}さん\n私の相談に乗ることを許しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve decided‚ {user}-san.\nI’m going to allow you to give me advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どうして上から目線なんだ……\nでも悩み事なら相談に乗るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with the high-handed tone?\nBut if something’s worrying you‚ you can talk to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "スタイルを良くするには\nどうすればいいんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do to\nimprove my figure?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "私、お顔はこんなに整っているのに\nなかなか理想のプロポーションになりませんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My face is already perfect‚\nbut I can’t get my body to the ideal proportions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様のように女性らしくすらっとしていれば\n圧倒的な差でアイドル界を席巻出来るはずなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I were as ladylike and slender as Mana-sama‚\nI’d be able to dominate the idol world with ease.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに牛乳は試しましたわ。練乳、豆乳、いちご牛乳\nチーズにヨーグルト、ラクトアイスに生バター……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I tried milk. Condensed milk‚ soy milk‚ strawberry milk‚\ncheese and yoghurt‚ milk ice cream and raw butter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "ありとあらゆる乳製品を摂取しまくりましたが\n……いま一つ、成長した気がしないのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been stuffing myself with all kinds of dairy products‚\nbut I still don’t feel as if I grew at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……そんなすぐに効果が出るものじゃ\nないんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… surely the effects don’t\nshow up that quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "……閃きましたわ\nいちご大福なら効果がありそうな気がしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got an idea!\nI get the feeling strawberry daifuku would have an effect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "あのぷりっとした見た目は、女性らしい\nプロポーションに効果的なのでは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That soft and rounded look might help\nme to get more feminine proportions‚ maybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "どんな理屈なんだ……なあ、すず\n無理に背伸びをする必要はないんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really‚ Suzu‚ I don’t see the logic there.\nDo you have to push yourself that much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "……背伸び、ですって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Push myself‚ you say…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。どんなアイドルにも長所と短所がある\nもちろん麻奈にない、すずだけの魅力だってある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Every idol has her strengths and weaknesses.\nI’m sure you have some appeal of your own that Mana lacked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "背伸びするんじゃなくて、一つ一つ\n自分の目の高さにある長所を見つけていけばいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather than trying to get taller‚ it would be better\nto find the strengths that only you have.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……あなた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "何も分かっていませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "really don’t understand anything‚ do you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……ええっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "あなた、麻奈様のそばで何を見ていたんですの？\n麻奈様に限って弱点などありえませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you blind when you were around Mana-sama?\nMana-sama alone of all people couldn’t have any weaknesses!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "あの方こそ、アイドルという山の頂\n一点の曇りもない、究極の存在！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was the pinnacle of all idols.\nThe ultimate presence‚ unblemished in the slightest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく！　「自分の目の高さにある長所」\nなんて甘えたことは言っていられませんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I don’t want sweet talk like\n“the strengths that only you have.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz024.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルたる者、上を目指して当たり前\n理想のプロポーションも必ず手に入れてみせますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s only natural for an idol to aspire to greater level‚\nand I am absolutely going to get to the ideal proportions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz025.m4a",
      "text": "ですから\n改めて……秘訣を教えなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I wanted you\ntell me the secret trick.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-suz026.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルのマネージャーなのですから\n当然、そのくらい知っていますわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re a manager of idols‚\nso surely you know at least that much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
