      "text": "……寝る子は育つというからな\nやっぱりよく食べ、よく寝るのが近道じゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say “sleep brings a child up well”‚\nso maybe eating and sleeping well might be a shortcut after all.",
        "id": ""
