      },
      "startTime": 203.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。もちろん、ただ食べるだけじゃなくて\nちゃんと栄養バランスも考えなきゃな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup. Of course it’s not just about eating.\nYou also have to think about the right nutritional balance.",
