      "text": "……なるほど\n思っていたよりマトモなこと言いますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nThat makes more sense than I was expecting from you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
